<p><b>Dewey's Complete Writings</b> is available in 3 multi-volume sets (37 volumes in all) from <a href="http://www.siu.edu/~siupress" class="external text" title="http://www.siu.edu/~siupress" rel="nofollow">Southern Illinois University Press</a>:</p>
<ul>
<li><i>The Early Works: 1892-1898</i> (5 volumes)</li>
<li><i>The Middle Works: 1899-1924</i> (15 volumes)</li>
<li><i>The Later Works: 1925-1953</i> (17 volumes)</li>
</ul>
<p><b>The Correspondence of John Dewey</b> is available on <a href="http://www.nlx.com/titles/titldewc.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.nlx.com/titles/titldewc.htm" rel="nofollow">CD-ROM</a> in 3 volumes.</p>
